    {
      "heading": "Best practices",
      "level": 2,
      "anchor": "Best-practices",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "**Use secure digit fields.** Secure digit fields display asterisks instead of the entered digit onscreen. Always use a secure digit field when your app asks for sensitive data."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "**Clearly state the purpose of the digit entry view.** Use a title and prompt that explains why someone needs to enter digits."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
